* Security *
	- Need to test upgrade after raising secure level to 1 (direct access to /dev)
	- System fingerprint:
	Use mtree for generate the fingerprint of the base system
	mtree -c -K sha256digest > mtree.txt
	And store the result on a reference website, then create a script that download it and compare it:
	mtree -f /path/to/mtree.txt -K sha256digest

